text:
New photos from Pluto 'astonish' NASA scientists More photos of the distant dwarf planet continue to roll in from NASA's New Horizons spacecraft. Check out this story on WHAS11.com: http://usat.ly/1FiUbpm Pluto is the gift that keeps on giving as more photos from the distant dwarf planet continue to roll in from NASA's New Horizons spacecraft.
